caption.p: Analysis of Molecular Dynamics Simulation results of free 3CLpro (Black), 3CLpro-Raltegravir complex (Red) and 3CLpro-Paritaprevir complex (turquoise). (a) Root Mean Square Deviation (RMSD), (b) Root Mean Square Fluctuation (RMSF), (c) Radius of Gyration (Rg), (d) Solvent Accessible Surface Area (SASA).
